readosm
------------------------------------------
ReadOSM is an open source library to extract valid data from within an Open
Street Map input file.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libexpat-devel-2.8.0-1
  libexpat1-2.8.0-1
  libreadosm-devel-1.1.0a-1bl2
  libreadosm1-1.1.0a-1bl2
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1
  zlib-devel-1.3.2-1
  zlib0-1.3.2-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  libexpat-devel-2.8.0-1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2
  zlib-devel-1.3.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://www.gaia-gis.it/fossil/readosm/index

Canonical download:
  https://www.gaia-gis.it/gaia-sins/readosm-1.1.0a.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack readosm-1.1.0a-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./readosm-1.1.0a-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/readosm-1.1.0a-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/readosm-1.1.0a-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libreadosm1-1.1.0a-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libreadosm-devel-1.1.0a-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(readosm)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/readosm.README
  /usr/share/doc/readosm/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/readosm/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/readosm/README

(libreadosm1)
  /usr/bin/cygreadosm-1.dll

(libreadosm-devel)
  /usr/include/readosm.h
  /usr/lib/libreadosm.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/readosm.pc

